&quot;Whats your poison&quot; asked a young bar maiden named Lydia Nyasin.  <br>
&quot;Just plain ale&quot; He replied, dropping a few plat on the table.  &quot;Keep'em comming&quot; he added.  Now after a long journey he sat down to relax hoping for a bit of rest before getting a room. <br>
